Dan kebersihan itu penting.

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:09.680
Itulah sebabnya.

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:11.760
Oke.  Bagus.

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:30.080
Mohan.

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:31.480
Mohan.

00:05:31.840 --> 00:05:33.080
Mohan...

