00:07:42.840 --> 00:07:45.680
Gungun, tolong tetap kuat.

00:07:45.760 --> 00:07:46.840
Silakan!

00:08:12.280 --> 00:08:13.560
Mohan, kumohon!

00:08:14.040 --> 00:08:16.880
