bagaimana Gungun bisa tetap kuat?

00:08:17.080 --> 00:08:18.200
Tolong, Mohan!

00:09:09.360 --> 00:09:11.280
Lihatlah dirimu sendiri, Radha.

00:09:12.760 --> 00:09:15.600
